snippet.title: Catly - Official Reveal Trailer | The Game Awards 2024
snippet.description:
Here's a first look at Catly in this reveal trailer for the upcoming interactive open-world adventure game starring beautiful and hyper-realistic cats. Catly will be available on Steam, Nintendo Switch, and Apple Watch in 2025. Catly is a love letter to cats, made for cat lovers by cat lovers. Every encounter celebrates cat mannerisms that showcase cats’ playfulness, grace, coziness, and of course, mischief.

#IGN #Gaming #TheGameAwards
